      "review_id": "Sygv6hHya7",
      "rebuttal_id": "rJlr5Z-t0Q",
      "sentence_index": 29,
      "text": "In this paper, we establish the linear convergence rate for the discretization error, which is highly trivial since the process has state-dependent jumps.",
